# RECODE - python code

### Installation

To install RECODE package, use `pip` as follows:

```
$ pip install screcode
```

### Documentation

[Tutorials and API reference](https://yusuke-imoto-lab.github.io/RECODE/index.html)


### Requirements
* Python3
* numpy
* scipy
* scikit-learn
